data.description: LOCATION meets LIFESTYLE! Own in the Heart of Hobe Sound overlooking a serene nature preserve in the community of Sugar Pines. This one story, single family, concrete home is the popular extended model, has a beautiful newer metal roof, PLUS a 2 car garage! This true 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom home has an awesome enclosed Florida Room, outdoor deck & built on a premium, cul-de-sac location. Resident Community Pool, Public Water & Sewer. Lower Taxes, Insurance & HOA fees are a plus in Martin County. Sugar Pines will handle your landscaping & community pool maintenance. Makes a perfect primary residence or winter retreat. Great public & private schools! Close to beaches, public & private golf courses, shopping, dining & entertainment. Endless opportunities for fun, welcome to your forever home.
